title: Bobby Cried In Front Of His Girlfriend + Raymundo’s Backup Wedding Plan + Bobby’s Mailbag: Can You Date Someone You Used To Babysit?
itunes:title: Bobby Cried In Front Of His Girlfriend + Raymundo’s Backup Wedding Plan + Bobby’s Mailbag: Can You Date Someone You Used To Babysit?
description:
Bobby watched something on the internet that made him so happy that he shed some tears in front of his girlfriend. Raymundo updates us on his wedding plans and details their plan if they still can’t have people attend in October due to the coronavirus. Plus, Bobby reads a listener's email question about dating someone you used to babysit!
